accessibility.text: You run madly for quiet a long way, breathing heavily and losing all the strength. Then you notice that darkness is falling again. Maybe it is the sunset of this strange land, or maybe it is caused by some other freaking creatures.
Suddenly, something grasps your left feet incredibly hard. You cannot control yourself and fall down onto some liquid land.
\"What the hell is it…?\" Now you are totally freaking out.
You are sinking down to a dark, viscous, living marsh.
